  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350\u00b0F (175\u00b0C).",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine the ginger cordial, gluten-free flour blend, almond meal, melted butter, vanilla extract, maple syrup, and cinnamon. Mix until well combined.",
    "Divide the batter into two portions and place each portion on a parchment-lined baking sheet.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds evenly over each portion of the batter.",
    "Bake in preheated oven for 18-20 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool slightly before serving."
